title: Wolves At The Gate Discography 2011-2013 (4 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
WOLVES AT THE GATE DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 4 releases...

 * 2011 - We Are The Ones
 * 2012 - Captors
 * 2012 - The King - Single
 * 2013 - Back To School EP

Wolves at the Gate is a Christian post-hardcore band from Cedarville, Ohio, United States. Formed circa 2009, they're currently signed to Solid State Records, where the band released two EPs: We Are the Ones (2011) and Back to School (2013), a full-length album: Captors (2012), and "The King" a 2012 Christmas single.

Glory Above,
TorrentTracts - October 2013
